soybeans %>% 
  ggplot(aes(DOY, yield))+
  geom_point(aes(fill = factor(Year)),shape = 21)+
  facet_wrap(~Loc)+
  scale_fill_manual(values = wesanderson::wes_palette("FantasticFox1"))+
  theme(aspect.ratio = .85,
                axis.title = element_text(size=14))
